{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-7", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "來信", "storyInfo": "雷爾金，我們到達了那裡。那個位於烏卡邊境的農莊，那個整合運動所在的地方，那個溫暖的……平等的理想之處。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g13_reunionfarm", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1", "style": "bgeffect", "name": "$eb_sunshine_upperedge", "slot": "bgover", "y": 100.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏卡邊境，荒地農莊</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_093#2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_004", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_093#2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_004", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……又是個晴天。我印象中這輩子真的沒有遇過幾次像這樣溫暖的冬天。", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多好啊……只要種下去的這批小麥能撐過冬天，中間不遇到天災……明年我們就能徹底自給自足了！", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_093#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "照之前的經驗來看，還是別高興得太早了……", "name": "擔憂的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_093#2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_004", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "婆婆，樂觀一點！以前我們不是都還以為自己無處可去，會死在荒野上嗎？現在卻有了農莊，有房子住，有熱粥喝——", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，那邊好像是……", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是塔露拉小姐，還有九小姐！", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hidehaystack", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_004"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉小姐，你們是在幫忙拔掉雜草嗎？", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉，有人在跟你說話。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，沒錯。是我哪裡做得不對嗎？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看其他人也在做，而且這些雜草確實長得太高了，這樣看不清楚麥子的生長情況。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_004"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，這是對的。除掉雜草可以保證小麥有足夠的養分越冬——", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您真聰明！", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_004"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們已經拔了這麼多了，而且沒有誤傷麥苗，看來不用我幫忙了。", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這方面，你是一位經驗豐富的老師。雅各布最近怎麼樣了？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_004"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "託你們的福，那些新藥都很有效！他已經很久沒有半夜痛到從床板上掉下去了。", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要注意防護。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_004"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我知道。還能和他像這樣在一起，已經比我曾經所有的想像都好了。", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你們，謝謝整合運動！", "name": "喜悅的農婦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_004"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不客氣。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#10$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩年了，你還是不太習慣收到別人的感謝。", "name": "九"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你早該習以為常了。", "name": "九"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他們應該感謝的其實不是我。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，當他們被團結在“整合運動”這面旗幟之下時，應該感謝的，其實是他們自己。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從廢墟裡重新建立生活的能力和勇氣，這不是誰都擁有的。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望他們能明白到這一點。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之前，你至少該讓自己在恍神被發現時表現得更自然點。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#2$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在想……暉潔下次什麼時候回來。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我你在擔心她。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她每次多多少少都會帶回一些新消息。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災信使不負責我們所處的這塊爭議地帶，普通的信使更不會路過，我們這兩年陸續建立的訊息網路還不夠健全。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在等……等暉潔帶來一些更接近真實的東西。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#3$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想聽到什麼？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是什麼……我想要瞭解現在的烏薩斯，此時此刻，正在真實發生的事。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不相信我們曾經在西部看到的那些場景。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你相信嗎？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#4$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上位者施捨的一點點仁慈就足以平息大部分的怒火，足以讓遭受不公的人們忘記思考、忘記反抗。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#4$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少我們確實沒有收到過來自礦區的求助，不管是來自西部還是更遠的地方。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#3$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許他們只是不知道我們的存在，或者無法到達這裡。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，我們也還沒有在此處建立起真正穩定的居所。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但已經在這裡的人並沒有因此對我們失望。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但他們應該失望的，九。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉回過頭去，看著太陽高高懸掛的方向。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她直視那道光，直到眼球刺痛。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "avgdisplay", "attributes": {"id": "1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_leavesfalling", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i19", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_breezeblow_amb", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "br"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "br", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "re"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "re", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "re", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是現在，我們的農莊幾乎能夠自給自足，一切卻仍然會因為一次可能的、無人預警的天災而頃刻間化為烏有。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最一開始的幾個月，我們不斷經歷這樣的損失。在無數次的摸索後，我們才來到了這裡，收穫了這樣的安寧。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它畢竟是無法長久的。我也曾以為在一次次的輾轉中，離開我們的同行者會比留下的更多，卻沒想到隊伍越來越壯大。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且還不是因為受到壓迫的人變多了，而是因為選擇了我們的人沒有失望地離去，即使他們應該。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是嘗試主動向他們釋放善意，多數人卻都選擇了報以始終如一的信任。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當活著的苦痛已經無數次壓垮這些人之後，他們貧瘠的土地上竟然還能捧出這樣比黃金更寶貴的情感？", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能……在那些事之後，我無法想像。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "九"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我開始思考……如果這就是事物發展的規律呢？這些最質樸的人們所相信的真理，也不過如此。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跌倒，而後重新站起；失敗，而後從頭再來。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底想說什麼？", "name": "九"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還會失敗，九。但我認為，現在我們已經能夠不為此感到憂懼。", "name": "塔露拉"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "br", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g13_reunionfarm", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你錯了。我從未因此感到憂懼。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但與我們同行的人曾有過，畢竟不是所有人都像你一樣，心中總有那些遠大的展望，許多人只想要看見明天的太陽。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九，新的抑制劑生產線已經完成了，我們現在就開始使用嗎？", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦利亞。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我說，我們現在要放棄這裡，前往聖駿堡，你會怎麼做？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還用問嗎？當然是跟你們一起啊。", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他人呢？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一樣。我們早就知道，整合運動是不會止步於此的。", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，最好不是所有人都走吧。現在大家都各司其職地工作一段時間了，有戰鬥能力的跟你們去，其他人還是可以待在後方啊。", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_080"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "感染者戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_080"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九，就像他說的那樣……我覺得，現在我們也許已經準備好了——", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準備好面對那些如今還隱藏在光鮮背後的醜惡。如果它由來已久、枝蔓龐雜，無人能夠將它一次就連根拔起……", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就拔第二次、第三次……只要還有人活著，直到有人成功。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我們已經知道了應該團結的人是誰，如果打破枷鎖的時刻到來了，我們就要毫不猶豫地去做。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "團結所有能夠團結的人，打破所有原本不應加身的鎖鏈……", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只需等待一個時機。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉、九。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有緊急的事。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷德，怎麼了？很少看到你這麼緊張。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1983_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在農莊附近遇到了一批難民，他們說自己是從遠北逃難出來的礦工，是為了“整合運動”這個名字過來的。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確認過身分，他們沒有帶武器，都是感染者——我讓他們先在崗哨那裡等著了，後續到底怎麼做，需要由你們決定。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠北？之前我們沒有得到過太多關於遠北的消息，他們說的逃難又是指什麼？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，就是那個消息被封得像鐵桶一樣嚴密的遠北。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於發生了什麼，還是讓親歷者來跟你說吧。", "name": "雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_328_1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝……謝謝你們的收留……好心的女士、先生……你們就是“整合運動”嗎？", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的沒有想到……雷爾金說的是真的……我的天啊……", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別著急，我們是整合運動，我們會努力幫助每一位受苦的同胞。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以請你先告訴我，你們都遭遇了什麼嗎？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1968_1#6$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在遠北……遭遇了一場屠殺……", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}